    "In this architecture, the values coming from the lower layer are concatenated with the data coming from the attention structure at the same level as itself.",
    "Then, the incoming data are transferred to the next layer by applying the up sample process.",
    "The same operations are repeated until the Block_De_1 structure.",
    "The sizes of all outputs produced by the system up to the Block_De_1 structure are also presented in Table 1.",
    "After this process, the values obtained from each block level are transferred to the output layer."
